# Health & Execution Endpoints
# Select environment: View > Command Palette > "Rest Client: Switch Environment" -> local | dev

### Health check (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health


### List available scripts
GET {{baseUrl}}/scripts
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}


### Execute a script
# @name execute
POST {{baseUrl}}/execute
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "target": {
    "type": "script",
    "name": "test.echo",
    "version": "2026.04.18"
  },
  "input": {
    "message": "hello from REST Client"
  }
}


### Get a specific execution record
GET {{baseUrl}}/executions/{{executionId}}
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}


### Query execution records (optional filters: script_name, status, limit)
GET {{baseUrl}}/executions?limit=20
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}


### Replay a previous execution
POST {{baseUrl}}/executions/{{executionId}}/replay
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{}
